Turns outhe's from corpus christi.

15:35.613 --> 15:37.316
Name is gordon laroche.

15:37.612 --> 15:39.628
And seeing
as he was 59instead of 20 like

15:39.628 --> 15:41.503
the guy you dreamed about,I figured that

15:41.503 --> 15:43.613
maybe you were wrongabout everything.

