Well, I guess I was.

15:45.925 --> 15:49.237
This guy laroche must've had
the same tattoo as theman I dreamt about.

15:50.050 --> 15:53.487
Well, this is great news.
Thank you.

15:53.487 --> 15:56.550
Okay, so I never reached outto mr. Reshmi.

15:57.237 --> 15:59.237
Would you have spentthe afternoon dialing india?

15:59.347 --> 16:01.999
No, probably not, but I wouldn'thave told our daughter

16:01.999 --> 16:03.441
I was going to do itin the first place.

